          <b>"How do I use those smiley icons?"</b>
          <blockquote>
          
   You can imbedd emotion icons by typing a combination of
   special characters.  For example, to imbedd <img src="http://www.kaaos.com/htdocs/dcforum/Images/happy.gif">
   you would type :-).  There are a dozen or so emotion icons which are
   listed in this
   <a href="javascript:makeRemote('http://www.kaaos.com/cgi-bin/dcforum/dcboard.cgi?az=emotion_icon_short_cuts')">
      emotion icon short cuts table</a>.
   
